ie_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;👇🏻&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;（健康中国）&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hoftyamltgj20m81ub465.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/O8imam0T5</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/O8imam0T5</guid><pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 04:12:28 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item><item><title>挠到出血还是痒痒痒[裂开]，多少人被湿疹坑到崩溃？想快点好，先搞清楚这7个误区[苦涩]👇🏻#小卫唠健康##小卫来辟谣#（四川大学华西医院） [图片][图片][图...</title><description>挠到出血还是痒痒痒&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[裂开]&quot; src=&quot;https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;，多少人被湿疹坑到崩溃？想快点好，先搞清楚这7个误区&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[苦涩]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/7e/2021_bitter_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;👇🏻&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&quot